---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import heroPiano from "../../assets/images/hero-piano.webp";
---

<section
    class="relative min-h-[80vh] py-20 md:py-0 md:h-[85vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden"
>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
        <Image
            src={heroPiano}
            alt="落ち着いた空間でのピアノレッスン"
            width={1200}
            height={800}
            class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-50"
            loading="eager"
            fetchpriority="high"
        />
        <div
            class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#FCFAF7]/20 to-[#FCFAF7]"
        >
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-6 md:px-4 max-w-5xl">
        <span
            class="block text-xs md:text-sm tracking-[0.15em] md:tracking-[0.2em] leading-relaxed mb-6 text-[#544A40] font-serif font-bold uppercase"
        >
            <span class="inline-block">東京都内</span><span class="inline-block">（江東区・中央区周辺）</span><span class="inline-block">出張・スタジオ対応</span>
        </span>

        <h1 class="font-serif text-[#544A40] flex flex-col items-center">
            <span
                class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl tracking-[0.1em] sm:tracking-[0.15em] text-[#433D3C] font-bold mb-3 sm:mb-4"
                >大人のための出張ピアノレッスン</span
            >

            <span
                class="block text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-medium tracking-normal sm:tracking-normal mb-6 sm:mb-8 leading-tight text-[#333333]"
            >
                髙橋遊月ピアノ教室
            </span>
        </h1>
        <p
            class="font-serif text-sm md:text-base leading-[1.9] md:leading-[2.2] tracking-wider md:tracking-widest text-[#544A40] max-w-2xl mx-auto font-medium"
        >
            <span class="block md:inline-block">ご自宅や近隣スタジオへ講師がお伺いします。</span>
            <br class="hidden md:inline" />
            <span class="block md:inline-block mt-3 md:mt-0">楽譜が読めない初心者の方から、ブランクのある再開者の方まで。</span>
            <br class="hidden md:inline" />
            <span class="block md:inline-block mt-3 md:mt-0">受講頻度・曲目・進め方は、ご希望に合わせて相談しながら進めます。</span>
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 sm:mt-12 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center w-full max-w-md mx-auto sm:max-w-none px-4 sm:px-0">
            <a
                href="https://lin.ee/QL31tIZ"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="inline-block bg-[#06C755] hover:bg-[#05b34c] text-white font-bold px-6 py-3.5 sm:px-8 sm:py-4 rounded-full shadow-lg transition-transform transform hover:-translate-y-0.5 text-sm sm:text-base w-full sm:w-auto text-center"
            >
                まずは体験レッスンをLINEで相談する
            </a>
            <a
                href="#area"
                class="inline-block bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 text-[#544A40] border border-[#8B7355] font-bold px-6 py-3.5 sm:px-8 sm:py-4 rounded-full shadow-md transition-transform transform hover:-translate-y-0.5 text-sm sm:text-base w-full sm:w-auto text-center"
            >
                対応エリアを確認する
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
